    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Shadow Prisoner&quot; is a 2D fighting game with simple controls that allow you to perform exhilarating combos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can play with 25 characters (9 will be added for free, and one is a collaboration character that will be paid DLC).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even if you have no experience with fighting games, you can use the simple mode to play like an experienced fighting gamer just by repeatedly pressing buttons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are story mode and survival mode for single player, and versus mode and network mode for competitive play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Network mode has a zero-latency netcode that supports rollback.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are playing in Japan, you can play with the same input sensation as if you were playing next to someone in Japan.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Currently available is the main game and the additional non-combo game April Liars.</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition, Epsilon mode, a fighting action game where you shoot each other with a barrage of bullets, exclusive to the Steam version, will be added.</p>",
